{
  "texts": [
    "They cannot be moved if they are processing or in transport already.",
    "For ease of computing, the shop floor is discretized as a grid that restricts the final position of entities to intersections on the grid.",
    "The number of stations in the assembly system is given a priori to the simulation start.",
    "Despite that, a station can break down and be out of order for a particular time.",
    "The interval between breakdowns is denoted by the mean time between failures for every station."
  ]
}